 was also the name of the wife of  Henry VI  of England,  Margaret of Anjou  (  1430–82 ), and of  Margaret Tudor  (  1489–1541 ), sister of  Henry VIII , who married James IV of Scotland and ruled as regent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."]},{"name":"Margareta","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margarethe","meanings":["from Greek.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1353607,"age":25,"year":"1536","julianDay":2282072,"description":"Switzerland is a loose confederacy of 13 cities and small valley communities dominating the rest of the country. A few families control state affairs. Several rebellions put down by military force: repressed aspects of history in a country so proud of it's tradition of democracy.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Margaretha Brandenberg was born about 1511, in Zug, Zug, Switzerland as the daughter of Hans Brandenberg. She had at least 1 son with Jacob Speck."},"et":{"um 1511–":"umbes 1511–Surnud","1511–Female":"1511–Surnud","1518–Male":"1518–Surnud","1530–Male":"1530–Surnud","1490–Male":"1490–Surnud","1536":"1536","1511":"1511","1530":"1530","1518":"1518","1490":"1490","um 1511":"umbes 1511","Zug, Kt. Zug, Schweiz":"Zug, Zug, Šveits","Zug, Zug, Switzerland":"Zug, Zug, Šveits"},"fi":{"um 1511–":"noin 1511–Kuollut","1511–Female":"1511–Kuollut","1518–Male":"1518–Kuollut","1530–Male":"1530–Kuollut","1490–Male":"1490–Kuollut","1536":"1536","1511":"1511","1530":"1530","1518":"1518","1490":"1490","um 1511":"noin 1511","Zug, Kt. Zug, Schweiz":"Zug, Zug, Sveitsi","Zug, Zug, Switzerland":"Zug, Zug, Sveitsi"},"fr":{"um 1511–":"environ 1511–Décédée","1511–Female":"1511–Décédée","1518–Male":"1518–Décédé","1530–Male":"1530–Décédé","1490–Male":"1490–Décédé","1536":"1536","1511":"1511","1530":"1530","1518":"1518","1490":"1490","um 1511":"environ 1511","Zug, Kt. Zug, Schweiz":"Zug, Zoug, Suisse","Zug, Zug, Switzerland":"Zug, Zoug, Suisse","l